X = NOUS
V = VIDE
O = L'ADV

DANGER
5  [O O O O O]		1 Translation
4  [V O O O O V]	1 Translation
4  [V O O O O X]	2 Translation
4  [O V O O O]		2 Translation
4  [O O V O O]		1 Translation
3l [V O O O V]		1 Translation
3l [V O V O O V]	2 Translation
3  [O O V V O]		2 Translation
2  [V O O V]		1 Translation
2  [V V V O O X]	2 Translation
p  [O X X V]		2 Translation // (L'IMPORTANCE DEPEND DU SCORE ACTUEL)
		       ___
			17 -> 5bit

INTERET
5  [X X X X X]		1 Translation
4  [V X X X X V]	1 Translation
4  [V X X X X O]	2 Translation
4  [X V X X X]		2 Translation
4  [X X V X X]		1 Translation
3l [V X X X V]		1 Translation
3l [V X V X X V]	2 Translation
3  [V X X V V X V]	2 Translation
2  [V X X V]		1 Translation
2  [V V V X X O]	2 Translation
p  [X O O V]		2 Translation // (L'IMPORTANCE DEPEND DU SCORE ACTUEL)
		       ___
			17

