2  vert 1		||  3  pattern (0 | 1 | 2 | 3 | 3l | 4 | 5 | prenable)
2  vert 2		||  3  pattern (0 | 1 | 2 | 3 | 3l | 4 | 5 | prenable)
2  diag \ 1		||  3  pattern (0 | 1 | 2 | 3 | 3l | 4 | 5 | prenable)
2  diag \ 2		||  3  pattern (0 | 1 | 2 | 3 | 3l | 4 | 5 | prenable)
2  diag / 1		||  3  pattern (0 | 1 | 2 | 3 | 3l | 4 | 5 | prenable)
2  diag / 2		||  3  pattern (0 | 1 | 2 | 3 | 3l | 4 | 5 | prenable)
